<% unless @user.name.nil? %>Hi <%= @user.name %>,<% else %>Hi there,<% end %>

This week on Falling Fruit, there were <%= @changes.length %> changes in your foraging range: 

<% 
  hist = {}
  @changes.each{ |c| 
    c.location.types.each{ |t|
      next if t.nil?
      t = t.name
      hist[t] = 0 if hist[t].nil?
      hist[t] += 1
    }
  %>
  * <%= c.location.title %> <%= c.description %>: http://fallingfruit.org/locations/<%= c.location.id %>
<% } %>

The number of new locations, by type: 

<%= hist.collect{ |k,v| "#{k}: #{v}" }.join("\n") %>

Thanks for contributing to the map! Have an awesome week.

